- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely because the paper discusses the relationships between different actors in the innovation system. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possibility because the paper may discuss software tools or platforms used in open innovation or triple helix models. 
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is a possibility because the paper may use computational methods to measure the synergy in innovation systems. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is a possibility because the paper may discuss the role of human factors in open innovation or triple helix models.
